**ttak_tam_tam**
- [ namaṭṭuccoṟi ]
பெ. id.+
1. itch
scabies; சிரங்கு
2. papular eruption of the skin
of which violent and chronicitching is the chief symptom
prurigo; சொறிபுண்
3. cutaneous disease with glisteningimbricated scales affecting only the superficial layers of the skin
psoriasis; சிரங்கு வகை

**சென்னைப் பல்கலைக்கழகத் தமிழ்ப் பேரகராதி**
- - namaṭṭu-c-coṟi;
- n. <</>id.+.
- 1. Itch;  scabies;
- சிரங்கு;
- 2. Papular eruption of the skin;  of which violent and chronic itching is the chief symptom;  prurigo;
- சொறி புண்.
- 3. Cutaneous disease with glistening imbricated scales affecting only the superficial layers of the skin;  psoriasis;
- சிரங்கு வகை.

